(Az TA.) ―         -b4-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin with which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafon","text_ar":"جَفْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scabbard"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a sword is covered, from the lower part of its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aArib","text_ar":"شَارِب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEol","text_ar":"نَعْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shoe of iron,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver, at the lower end of the scabbard"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering that is put upon the hilt, consisting of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the skins called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaAn","text_ar":"اَسْفَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safanN","text_ar":"سَفَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]: (K. [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaAn","text_ar":"اَسْفَان"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the reading in the M, some copies of the K have"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaAr","text_ar":"اَسْفَار"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sword,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of what is next to thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when holding the hilt"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and sometimes it signifies its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimod","text_ar":"غِمْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scabbard"},{"kind":"text","text":"], also. (Ham p. 22.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaA$iyapu","text_ar":"الغَاشِيَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in the Kur lxxxviii. I, TA) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The resurrection;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) because it will overwhelm (↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tago$aY","text_ar":"تَغْشَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":") with its terrors; (S, TA;) or because it will come upon mankind as a thing covering them, (↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tago$aY","text_ar":"تَغْشَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxaloqa","text_ar":"الخَلْقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) so as to include them universally: (TA:) and, (K, TA,) some say, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fire of Hell"},{"kind":"text","text":"); (K, TA;) because it will cover, or overspread, (↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tago$aY","text_ar":"تَغْشَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",) the faces of the unbelievers. (TA.) (In like manner also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaA$iyapN mina AlEa*aAbi","text_ar":"غَاشِيَةٌ مِنَ العَذَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Punishment that is general,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"universal, in its extent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaA$iyapN","text_ar":"غَاشِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cer tain disease that attacks in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawof","text_ar":"جَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (As, S, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaAhu A@ll~`hu bigaA$iyapK","text_ar":"رَمَاهُ ا@للّٰهُ بِغَاشِيَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God smite him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afflict him, with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaA$iyap","text_ar":"غَاشِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (As, S.) ―         -b8-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Petitioners that come to one"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demanding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asking, gifts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"visiters, and friends, that come to one time after time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that resort to one"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resorters;"},{"kind":"text","text":"such as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guests;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hangers-on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seekers of favours; servants"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dependants"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"others."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har pp. 95 and 467.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S"]}]}}